{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 9,
  "title": "第九章（持盈）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "持而盈之，不若亓已。"
    },
    {
      "text": "揣而銳之，不可常葆之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "金玉盈室，莫之守也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "貴富而驕，自遺咎也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "功述身芮，天之道也。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "盈，滿也。已，止也。持滿必傾，不如止也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "揣，治也。先揣之，後必棄捐。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "嗜慾傷神，財多累身。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫富當賑貧，貴當憐賤，而反驕恣，必被禍患也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言人所為，功成事立，名蹟稱遂，不退身避位，則遇於害，此乃天之常道也。譬如日中則移，月滿則虧，物盛則衰，樂極則哀。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "持，謂不失德也。既不失其德又盈之，勢必傾危。故不如其已者，謂乃更不如無德無功者也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "既揣末令尖，又銳之令利，勢必摧衂，故不可長保也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不若其已。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不可長保也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "四時更運，功成則移。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
